comment4.text=\r\n\ A\ modification\ of\ the\ movementAnimation()\ method\ from\ Entity,\ overridden\ here\ to\ match\ with\ the\ Enemy's\ cycle\ method,\ as\ well\ as\ their\ lack\ of\ sprites\ for\ moving\ up\ and\ down.\r\n
