comment6.params=range
comment6.target=void\ findTarget(int)
comment6.text=\r\n\ A\ small\ recursive\ method\ that\ looks\ for\ targets,\ broadening\ its\ range\ until\ it\ finds\ a\ Villager\ in\ 200\ unit\ increments\ of\ range.\r\n
comment7.params=
comment7.target=void\ findTarget()
comment7.text=\r\n\ A\ small\ method\ that\ quickly\ finds\ any\ villager\ within\ a\ range\ of\ 2000\ and\ designates\ that\ one\ as\ the\ 'target',\ for\ use\ in\ subclass\ behaviours.\r\n\ The\ 'target'\ variable\ is\ used\ in\ a\ variety\ of\ different\ behaviours\ for\ the\ Enemy,\ but\ is\ more\ or\ less\ the\ one\ the\ Enemy\ tries\ to\ attack\ and\ seek\ out\ at\ most\ times.\r\n
comment8.params=
comment8.target=void\ act()
comment8.text=\r\n\ Enemy's\ act()\ method\ only\ calls\ super.act(),\ which\ in\ itself\ is\ in\ Entity,\ and\ calls\ the\ walk()\ method.\r\n
